data.description: $10,000 Price Improvement!! Huge, corner lot w/ RV parking! This spacious 3bdrm home is move-in ready. Previously renovated it boasts beautiful wood laminate flooring, new carpet in the bedrooms, new evaporative cooler & a new water heater. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel stove, & sink. Won't last long, lots of space for a great price!
